{
  "message": "fuzz(fj-conformance): add 35 corpus seeds for shape_inference_engine\n\nExtends fuzzer corpus from 22 to 57 seeds targeting:\n- Linalg: QR, SVD, Eigh, Cholesky, TriangularSolve\n- FFT: FFT, IFFT, RFFT, IRFFT\n- Complex: Complex, Conj, Real, Imag\n- Control flow: Cond, Scan, While, Switch\n- Gather/Scatter with 2D operands\n- Reductions with various axes\n- ReduceWindow, Conv (1D and 2D)\n- Tensor ops: Split, Pad, Rev, Squeeze, ExpandDims\n- Cumulative: Cumsum, Cumprod\n- Sorting: Sort, Argsort\n- OneHot\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
